text: Sharif Uddin Ahmed was a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Habiganj-2. ==Career== Ahmed was elected to parliament from Habiganj-2 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1991 and 1996. ==Death== Ahmed died in 1997. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:1997 deaths Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members
title: Sharif Uddin Ahmed
